			<h1 >Welcome to nuTriton</h1>
			<br/>
			<p>The one-stop place to find the foods suitable for your diet.</p>
			<p> Connect with others of the same dietary restrictions, share what's new in your life.</p>
		</div> 	
	</div>

	<div class="container">
		<div class="panel panel-default ">
			<div class="panel-body">
				<form >
				    <div class="form-group">
				    	<h3>Register</h3>
				    	<br/>
